original_title: Ultimate Smashdown Online #3 | Winners Quarters - RIGONARDO (Ganondorf) Vs. LegolaS (Ryu)
overview: A battle of a lifetime. This film pairs our protagonist, Lucho/Poseidon, who is known to be thriving (encarando) at this game against the evil RIGONARDO, master of deceit, teabags, and lag. Once close friends, they must now face each other against all odds, but only one can come victorious.
title: Ultimate Smashdown Online #3 | Winners Quarters - RIGONARDO (Ganondorf) Vs. LegolaS (Ryu)
